headline: Nvidia Stock Rises Ahead of Earnings Report
summary: Nvidia stock was gaining early on Wednesday. The chip maker is looking to snap a streak of losses ahead of its earnings report after the market closes. The shares were up 1.8% at $184.62 in premarket trading.

headline: Here’s How Options Traders Are Betting On Nvidia
summary: Options traders anticipate big moves in Nvidia shares after its earnings drop on Wednesday afternoon.   Traders are positioning for a roughly 8% swing in the share price, higher or lower, after earnings and through Friday, according to Cboe Global Markets data.
